# pre-commit: fast, staged-files-only auto-fix.
# Runs lint-staged which applies `prettier --write` + `eslint --fix` to the
# files in the index. This guarantees the exact failure that broke CI before
# (prettier --check on the v5 suite) can never be committed again. The full
# test suite is intentionally NOT run here to keep commits fast — it runs in
# the pre-push hook (mirroring the CI quality gate) instead.
npx lint-staged
